title: Best of Clancy And The Rockets Week 5: Dana White, Biznasty, Barstool Christmas Party, and the Ball In Cup League
description:
Clancy, Carrabis, and Kayce interview Dana White (3:30), celebrate the Miami Miracle and the Victory Worm (42:45), chat with Paul "Biznasty" Bissonette (56:30), drink some bowls of wine (1:10:00), recap the Barstool Christmas party (1:13:30) and witness history in the Ball in Cup League (1:47:20)


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
